In re County Treasurer. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. March 15, 1892.) Proceeding for the appointment of a referee to examine accounts of the county treasurer.

Argued before Mayham, P. J., and Putnam and Herrick, JJ.

Ho opinion. Ordered that James J. Farren of the city of Albany be and hereby is appointed a referee to examine county treasurer’s accounts. Order to be settled and entered by Herrick, J.
